Technician - Class in scheduler
The Technician class is an abstract subclass of Provider It represents a technician who has a fixed rate per visit It does not calculate charges based on specialty as doctors do Instead, the rate is predetermined and fixed per visit This class also supports the creation of the circular linked list of Technicians
